Lingua-ConText version 0.01
===========================

This module implements Wendy Chapman's ConText algorithm in perl. Info available at:

http://code.google.com/p/negex/

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None.

